Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.88,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}連れ出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.88,0:03:54.50,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}真っ暗な雲が去って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:59.02,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}残した水面に　映る色は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.02,0:04:05.64,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨上がり　君は　君の目で答えを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:08.77,Yuri004-OP-JP,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}探してほしい
