Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:05.66,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}你所製作的　玻璃飾品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:09.46,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}指尖一觸　寸心如割
